# Broken Knowledge Base — KB Check Example 12
# Intentionally broken KB with various errors for check_kb() to detect.

# Facts
human(socrates)
human(plato)

# Error 1: Duplicate facts
human(socrates)
human(plato)

# Error 2: Rule references undefined predicate
mortal($x) IF human($x) AND alive($x)

# Error 3: Circular rule without base case
ancestor($x, $y) IF ancestor($x, $z) AND ancestor($z, $y)

# Error 4: Another undefined predicate in rule body
smart($x) IF intelligent($x)

? mortal($who)
